description:
It’s time to wake up America. #SayNoToBillGates #NoNewNormal #IDoNotConsent .
.
Yeah, this isn’t your typical post from me. Quite frankly..I try to stay away from posting my views on things because they are not in line with all of the other “influencers.” (Yuck hate that word. 🥴) Sorry if y’all were here for another sell out that’s trying to people please....I’m not it. I will NEVER post a #stayhome photo. .
.
I have to be honest here...from the beginning of this thing, something deep down inside of me had a crazy uneasy feeling about what we were being told by the United States government. Now, let me also let you know that I tried SO DANG HARD to be positive, look at things with an open mind, & see both sides.
.
.
Well, I’m siding with basic logic & common sense. There are only so many freedoms I will allow to be ripped away from me and my family. How far will you allow them to push before they’ve gone too far? #wakeupamerica .
.
Let’s make waves, listen to your natural instincts. Let’s end the stigma today that is around thinking for yourself. CREATE YOUR OWN POST & tag me for a shoutout! ♥️ *post inspired by @informedmothers .
.
🛑 IMPORTANT MESSAGE: Let me go ahead and address this in the caption so I don’t have to retype over & over! 🙈 This post is NOT intended to say Covid19 is not real, it is very real. Sending out prayers to anyone directly effected. This post is about certain people in the United States government trying to overstep. 💗
